Cell["\<\
Observe that the algorithm is not analysed for completeness, so we can not \
yet guarantee that all dependencies have been found. However, irreducible \
pieces with different valence can not be dependent.\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{
  3.544950967645297*^9, 3.5451138348862944`*^9, {3.5921205425164394`*^9, 
